OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781626273
OL,3,CTakeaway closed after health
OL,4,Cinspectors find 'serious mouse
OL,5,Cinfestation'
OL,7,FA takeaway in Portsmouth has been shut
OL,8,Fdown by the council after it posed 'an
OL,9,Fimminent risk to public health'.
OL,11,FPaanchi, on 234 Fratton Road in the
OL,12,Fcity, was found to be in an
OL,13,F'unacceptable condition' and also had
OL,14,Fan 'active mouse infestation'.
OL,16,FInspecting officers who visited the
OL,17,FIndian restaurant on 10 June found
OL,18,Fmouse droppings next to open food and
OL,19,Fcooking equipment, and were also
OL,20,Fconcerned that mouse urine was present
OL,21,Fon work surfaces.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
