OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781626273
OL,3,CTakeaway closed after health
OL,4,Cinspectors find 'serious mouse
OL,5,Cinfestation'
OL,7,FThey immediately served a Hygiene
OL,8,FEmergency Prohibition Order on the
OL,9,Fbusiness, forcing them to close until
OL,10,Fthe risk had been removed.
OL,12,FOn 12 June 2026 Portsmouth City
OL,13,FCouncil took Paanchi Portsmouth Ltd,
OL,14,Fwho operate the restaurant, to court.
OL,16,FOfficers applied for a Hygiene
OL,17,FEmergency Prohibition Order at
OL,18,FPortsmouth Magistrates' Court, which
OL,19,Fwas granted by the district judge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
