OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781626273
OL,3,CTakeaway closed after health
OL,4,Cinspectors find 'serious mouse
OL,5,Cinfestation'
OL,7,FPaanchi must now remain closed until
OL,8,Fthe council is satisfied the
OL,9,Finfestation has been eradicated and
OL,10,Fthe restaurant has been 'thoroughly
OL,11,Fcleaned', and no longer poses a risk
OL,12,Fto public health.
OL,14,FCouncillor Lee Hunt, Cabinet Member
OL,15,Ffor Community Safety, Leisure, and
OL,16,FSport, said: "The level of mouse
OL,17,Factivity identified posed a clear and
OL,18,Fimmediate risk to public health.
